data.description: Great Location! Beautiful home with lots of room for your family. Easy access to I20 and shopping. Home features 4BR, 2.5BA. It has a large kitchen with abundant counter space, separate family room and a breakfast area in the kitchen. Also you have a formal dining and living room/office. Master bath has a double vanity, shower and corner whirlpool tub. The basement is partially finished with much more space to finish for whatever you would like. Enjoy your deck and private fenced backyard.
